channel.title: COVID-19 data published to IATI: what do we know and what’s next?
channel.description: The IATI Secertariat has shared initial analysis that evaluates the progress made in publishing data on COVID-related activities to IATI and outlines upcoming work intended to increase the quality and quantity of this information. Please read the full newspost on the [IATI website](https://iatistandard.org/en/news/covid-19-data-published-to-iati-what-do-we-know-and-whats-next/).
